e (comedian)|Jason Love]] * [[Loni Love]] (born 1971) * [[Jon Lovitz]] (born 1957) * [[Mark Lowry]] (born 1958) * [[Matt Lucas]] (born 1974) * [[Joanna Lumley]] (born 1946) * [[John Lutz]] (born 1973) * [[Jane Lynch]] (born 1960) * [[Katherine Lynch]] (born 1972) * [[Stephen Lynch (musician)|Stephen Lynch]] (born 1971) * [[Paul Lynde]] (1926–1982) {{div col end}}
