er]] (born 1965) * [[Jerry Stiller]] (born 1927) * [[Matt Stone]] (born 1969) * [[Larry Storch]] (born 1923) * [[Ryan Stout]] (born 1982) * [[Cecily Strong]] (born 1984) * [[Jud Strunk]] (1936–1981) * [[Jason Sudeikis]] (born 1975) * [[Chris Sugden]] (born 1952) * [[Nicole Sullivan]] (born 1970) * [[Slim Summerville]] (1892–1946) * [[Nick Swardson]] (born 1976) * [[Jim Sweeney (comedian)|Jim Sweeney]] (born 1955) * [[Julia Sweeney]] (born 1959) * [[Terry Sweeney]] (born 1950) * [[Eric Sykes]] (1923–2012) * [[Wanda Sykes]] (born 1964) * [[Magda Szubanski]] (born 1961) {{div col end}}
